@AspireContainerStarter.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5269

### Submit a Calc1 job
POST {{AspireContainerStarter.Api_HostAddress}}/jobs/calc1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "taxYear": "2024",
  "entityId": "ENT-001",
  "submittedAt": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z"
}

###

### Submit a Calc2 job
POST {{AspireContainerStarter.Api_HostAddress}}/jobs/calc2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "taxYear": "2024",
  "stateCode": "CA",
  "entityId": "ENT-001",
  "submittedAt": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z"
}

